WEBVTT

1
00:19:12.600 --> 00:19:14.600 
但其实我的口音是乡下农民口音
but I actually speak with the accent of a peasant.

2
00:19:14.600 --> 00:19:16.480 
总之  我今早在巡逻时
Anyway, I walked my beat this morning,

3
00:19:16.480 --> 00:19:18.620 
特意用俄语跟几个人聊天
and I spoke to several people in Russian.

4
00:19:18.620 --> 00:19:21.330 
他们都觉得我很厉害  对我敞开心扉
They were so impressed, they opened up to me.

5
00:19:21.340 --> 00:19:24.180 
-我获得了好几条有用的线索  -太好啦
- I got a number of useful tips. - All right.

6
00:19:24.180 --> 00:19:26.540 
这都是因为我强迫你做了无趣的事
All because I made you do something tedious.

7
00:19:26.540 --> 00:19:28.630 
是单调而已  别毁了这气氛
Monotonous. Don't ruin this.

8
00:19:28.740 --> 00:19:31.140 
谢谢各位前来参加希契科克的离婚派对
Thanks for coming out to Hitchcock's divorce party.

9
00:19:31.140 --> 00:19:32.860 
你知道你又弄了个基佬蛋糕吧
You know you got another gay cake, right?

10
00:19:32.860 --> 00:19:33.570 
什么  不可能
What? No way.

11
00:19:33.570 --> 00:19:35.780 
上面写的是"兄弟  兄弟  兄弟"
It says "Boys! Boys! Boys!" on it.

12
00:19:35.780 --> 00:19:37.640 
因为我们是好兄弟啊
Because we're the boys.

13
00:19:37.840 --> 00:19:40.360 
各位  我想明白我和安娜之间是哪里出了问题了
Guys, I figured out what went wrong between Anna and me.

14
00:19:40.360 --> 00:19:42.410 
是因为我的工作  我是个工作狂
My job. I'm a workaholic!

15
00:19:42.410 --> 00:19:43.450 
不再是了
Not anymore.

